one_reviews_text: The game shows a chess set on a table but there is no way to interact with the board as your hands/controllers don't show. nor do any of the buttons do anything.
I have win.10 a1060 ibm cooler 850 watts of power,  not right. King inside a pawn, moves like a game of tag. and im using a mouse. I paid for oculus riff, im using it. Can't castle.
